
    Quiz: Beyonce and Emmeline Pankhurst - who links them?

        

    
        Today marks 100 years since women in the UK first voted in a general election. Emmeline Pankhurst led the British suffragette movement who helped women win the right to vote. Play this quiz to find out how seven boundary-breaking women connect her to Beyonce.
                
                
                
                
                
            
            
        
    
        
            
                
                    
        
                        
